(436, 3, '2017-05-17 13:30:16', '2017-05-17 08:00:16', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">BJP government has simplified the procedures in four areas only out of 11 indicators set by World Bank. These include </span><a href="http://www.doingbusiness.org/reforms/overview/economy/india"><span style="font-weight: 400;">paying taxes easier</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> by introducing electronic system for paying employees contributions, </span><a href="http://www.doingbusiness.org/reforms/overview/economy/india"><span style="font-weight: 400;">trading across borders</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> by means of single electronic gateway, simplifying </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">the process for getting an electricity connection by eliminating the internal wiring inspection by the Electrical Inspectorate </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">and the process of starting a new business </span><a href="http://www.businessmirror.com.ph/government-rolls-out-simplified-business-application-procedure-across-agencies/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">reducing</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> procedural requirement of 34 days to 8 days. </span>', 'Will ensure cutting the red tape, simplify the procedures & remove the bottlenecks', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'will-ensure-cutting-the-red-tape-simplify-the-procedures-remove-the-bottlenecks', '', '', '2017-05-18 18:04:22', '2017-05-18 12:34:22', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=436', 0, 'promise', '', 0);
