(451, 3, '2017-05-17 13:35:22', '2017-05-17 08:05:22', 'Under the Digital India initiative, the BJP government has launched many projects including:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://aview.in/who-we-are">Talk to Teacher</a>: An Immersive e-learning classroom.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.it.iitb.ac.in/nmeict/home.html">Aakash Education Portal</a>: To empower teachers through workshops using technology.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sakshat.ac.in/">Sakshat</a>: To enable ICT driven delivery in Higher Education.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://www.ebasta.in/content/about-ebasta">E Basta</a>: To make school books available in digital form.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://epathshala.nic.in/">E Pathshala</a>: Resources for students, teachers, researchers, and educators.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://shaalasiddhi.nuepa.org/">Shaala Siddhi</a>: For school evaluation</li>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.converge.saransh&amp;hl=en">Saransh</a>: To help schools identify areas of improvement in students, teachers, and curriculum.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nNo statistics about the usage of these portals are publicly available on the usage of the websites.', 'Establish a national E-Library to empower school teachers and students', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '445-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-17 13:35:22', '2017-05-17 08:05:22', '', 445, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/445-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
