(493, 3, '2017-05-17 16:57:12', '2017-05-17 11:27:12', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">No bill in this regard has been tabled in Parliament since BJP government has come to power. However, the ministry </span><a href="http://www.moef.nic.in/sites/default/files/ScanJobInvitation%20of%20comments%20Draft%20Environment%20Law.pdf"><span style="font-weight: 400;">drafted</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> a bill in this regard and uploaded on its website in October 2015 but no progress has been made since then. </span>', 'Frame the environment laws in a manner that provides no scope for confusion and will lead to speedy clearance of proposals without delay', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '484-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-17 16:57:12', '2017-05-17 11:27:12', '', 484, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/484-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
