(554, 3, '2017-05-17 17:48:56', '2017-05-17 12:18:56', 'Finance Minister  <a href="http://164.100.47.194/Loksabha/Questions/QResult15.aspx?qref=1389&amp;lsno=16">announced for setting up the university</a> in budget 2014-15 with a budgetary provision of Rs. 100 Crore. However, no progress has been made in this regard. In fact, in an answer to Parliamentary question in November 2015, the then Human Resource Development Minister Smriti Irani responded by clarifying that there is <a href="http://164.100.47.190/loksabhaquestions/annex/6/AU215.pdf">no proposal by the BJP government</a> to set up a Central University dedicated to the Himalayan Technology.\r\n\r\nSince a mere announcement in the absence of any progress on action, the performance of the BJP government in this regard is classified as "Yet to Start".', 'Establish a Central University dedicated to Himalayan Technology', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'establish-a-central-university-dedicated-to-himalayan-technology', '', '', '2017-05-19 00:52:23', '2017-05-18 19:22:23', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=554', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
