(558, 3, '2017-05-17 17:55:50', '2017-05-17 12:25:50', '<a href="http://www.pradhanmantriyojana.co.in/fasal-bima-beema/">The Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojna</a> was launched by the BJP government in January 2016 to provide <a href="http://www.clearias.com/pradhan-mantri-fasal-bima-yojana/">insurance support</a> to farmers. The scheme replaced the National Agriculture Insurance Scheme (NAIS). The government has increased the budget for the scheme by 64% from Rs. 5500 crores in 2016-17 to Rs. 9000 crores in Rs. 2017-18. The total funds released by the government under various crop insurance schemes has gone up from Rs. 2550 crores in 2013-14 to Rs. 7960 crores in 2016-17 (as of Dec 2016).\r\n\r\n<a href="http://agri-insurance.gov.in/Login.aspx#">National Crop Insurance Portal</a> was launched to facilitate the real-time flow of information among stakeholders and prompt service delivery.\r\n\r\nNorms have been relaxed to provide assistance to farmers in case of 33 percent crop loss resulting from natural calamities, instead of earlier benchmark of 50 percent.', 'Implement a farm insurance scheme to take care of crop loss due to unforeseen natural calamities', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'implement-a-farm-insurance-scheme-to-take-care-of-crop-loss-due-to-unforeseen-natural-calamities', '', '', '2017-05-17 17:55:50', '2017-05-17 12:25:50', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=558', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
(559, 3, '2017-05-17 17:55:50', '2017-05-17 12:25:50', '<a href="http://www.pradhanmantriyojana.co.in/fasal-bima-beema/">The Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojna</a> was launched by the BJP government in January 2016 to provide <a href="http://www.clearias.com/pradhan-mantri-fasal-bima-yojana/">insurance support</a> to farmers. The scheme replaced the National Agriculture Insurance Scheme (NAIS). The government has increased the budget for the scheme by 64% from Rs. 5500 crores in 2016-17 to Rs. 9000 crores in Rs. 2017-18. The total funds released by the government under various crop insurance schemes has gone up from Rs. 2550 crores in 2013-14 to Rs. 7960 crores in 2016-17 (as of Dec 2016).\r\n\r\n<a href="http://agri-insurance.gov.in/Login.aspx#">National Crop Insurance Portal</a> was launched to facilitate the real-time flow of information among stakeholders and prompt service delivery.\r\n\r\nNorms have been relaxed to provide assistance to farmers in case of 33 percent crop loss resulting from natural calamities, instead of earlier benchmark of 50 percent.', 'Implement a farm insurance scheme to take care of crop loss due to unforeseen natural calamities', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '558-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-17 17:55:50', '2017-05-17 12:25:50', '', 558, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/558-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(560, 3, '2017-05-17 17:58:44', '2017-05-17 12:28:44', 'The BJP government launched the <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=145074">Soil Health Card Scheme</a> (SHCS)  in <a href="http://indiatoday.intoday.in/education/story/pm-narendra-modi-launches-soil-health-card-scheme-for-farmers-in-rajasthan/1/419872.html">February 2015</a>. <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=160078">Rs. 126 crores</a> were released to all states under this scheme in 2016-17. The government has distributed <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=160078">6 crore soil health cards</a> against the target of 14 crore SHCs as of March 2017. The inadequacy of soil testing facilities has been cited the main reason for slow progress in the distribution of Soil Health Cards.\r\n\r\n380 static and 80 mobile<a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=153822"> new soil testing labs</a> have been sanctioned (as on 16.11.2016). 6308 mini soil testing labs have also been sanctioned under the scheme during 2016-17.', 'Introduce soil assessment based crop planning and setting up mobile soil testing labs', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'introduce-soil-assessment-based-crop-planning-and-setting-up-mobile-soil-testing-labs', '', '', '2017-05-17 17:58:44', '2017-05-17 12:28:44', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=560', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
