(617, 7, '2017-05-18 08:29:33', '2017-05-18 02:59:33', 'BJP government created a separate Ministry of AYUSH (Ayurveda, Yoga and Naturopathy, Unani, Siddha and Homoeopathy) to channelise the efforts to promote the non-allopathic system of medicines. Budget allocation to the ministry has consistently increased, from <a href="http://www.livemint.com/Politics/tr8SA0OgI7ibU8mPFLOs4J/Budget-allocation-of-AYUSH-ministry-hiked-by-8.html">Rs 1,326 crore in 2016-17 to Rs 1,428 crore in 2017-18.</a>', 'Will increase the public investment to promote Yoga and AYUSH', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'will-increase-the-public-investment-to-promote-yoga-and-ayush', '', '', '2017-05-18 08:29:33', '2017-05-18 02:59:33', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=617', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
(618, 7, '2017-05-18 08:29:33', '2017-05-18 02:59:33', 'BJP government created a separate Ministry of AYUSH (Ayurveda, Yoga and Naturopathy, Unani, Siddha and Homoeopathy) to channelise the efforts to promote the non-allopathic system of medicines. Budget allocation to the ministry has consistently increased, from <a href="http://www.livemint.com/Politics/tr8SA0OgI7ibU8mPFLOs4J/Budget-allocation-of-AYUSH-ministry-hiked-by-8.html">Rs 1,326 crore in 2016-17 to Rs 1,428 crore in 2017-18.</a>', 'Will increase the public investment to promote Yoga and AYUSH', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '617-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-18 08:29:33', '2017-05-18 02:59:33', '', 617, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/617-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(619, 7, '2017-05-18 08:30:45', '2017-05-18 03:00:45', 'The number of courses in Ayurveda, Unani and Siddha has <a href="http://ayush.gov.in/sites/default/files/ANNUAL%20R%20EPORT%202016-17%20ENGLISH.pdf">remain stagnant at 10</a> and no new courses have been added during the tenure of BJP government. No new integrated courses have been introduced in the field of <a href="http://ayush.gov.in/education/courses-and-study">Indian System of Medicine and modern science and Ayurgenomics</a>, as per AYUSH ministry records.\r\n\r\nNorth Eastern Institute of Ayurveda and Homeopathy was <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=155763">inaugurated at Shillong, in December, 2016</a>. All India Institute of Ayurveda, New Delhi has <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=160043">also become functional in 2016</a>. Another institute, <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=155005">North Eastern Institute of Folk Medicine (NEIFM), Pasighat, Arunachal Pradesh</a> is expected to become functional in 2017.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=156093">As per the education policy of AYUSH ministry</a>, permissions have been given to open new colleges of Ayurveda, Siddha and Unani and also increase the admission capacity of undergraduate courses. Permission has also been granted to open new PG courses in Ayurveda.', 'Will set up institutions of Indian System of Medicine. We will start integrated courses for Indian System of Medicine (ISM) and modern science and Ayurgenomics', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'will-set-up-institutions-of-indian-system-of-medicine-we-will-start-integrated-courses-for-indian-system-of-medicine-ism-and-modern-science-and-ayurgenomics', '', '', '2017-05-18 08:30:45', '2017-05-18 03:00:45', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=619', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
(620, 7, '2017-05-18 08:30:45', '2017-05-18 03:00:45', 'The number of courses in Ayurveda, Unani and Siddha has <a href="http://ayush.gov.in/sites/default/files/ANNUAL%20R%20EPORT%202016-17%20ENGLISH.pdf">remain stagnant at 10</a> and no new courses have been added during the tenure of BJP government. No new integrated courses have been introduced in the field of <a href="http://ayush.gov.in/education/courses-and-study">Indian System of Medicine and modern science and Ayurgenomics</a>, as per AYUSH ministry records.\r\n\r\nNorth Eastern Institute of Ayurveda and Homeopathy was <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=155763">inaugurated at Shillong, in December, 2016</a>. All India Institute of Ayurveda, New Delhi has <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=160043">also become functional in 2016</a>. Another institute, <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=155005">North Eastern Institute of Folk Medicine (NEIFM), Pasighat, Arunachal Pradesh</a> is expected to become functional in 2017.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=156093">As per the education policy of AYUSH ministry</a>, permissions have been given to open new colleges of Ayurveda, Siddha and Unani and also increase the admission capacity of undergraduate courses. Permission has also been granted to open new PG courses in Ayurveda.', 'Will set up institutions of Indian System of Medicine. We will start integrated courses for Indian System of Medicine (ISM) and modern science and Ayurgenomics', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '619-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-18 08:30:45', '2017-05-18 03:00:45', '', 619, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/619-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(621, 7, '2017-05-18 08:35:34', '2017-05-18 03:05:34', 'India’s malnutrition statistics present an alarming picture, where more than <a href="http://rchiips.org/NFHS/pdf/NFHS4/India.pdf">35% children are underweight</a> and <a href="http://businessworld.in/article/World-Health-Day-India-s-Health-Report-Is-Unhealthy-/07-04-2017-115929/">70% of children between the age group of six months to three years suffer from anaemia</a>.\r\n\r\nBudgetary allocation for Integrated Child Development Scheme (ICDS) has declined from <a href="http://www.downtoearth.org.in/blog/union-budget-2015-children-left-asking-for-their-dues-as-ever-48885">Rs 18,200 crore in 2014-15</a> to <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=157886">Rs 16,800 crore in 2017-18</a>. The number of Special Newborn Care Units have seen marginal improvement, from <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/mbErel.aspx?relid=133548">525 in 2013-14 to 602 in Dec, 2015</a>.\r\n\r\nMission Indradhanush, a programme for universal immunisation of children has resulted in <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=155854">increase of full immunisation coverage by about 5-7%.</a> Overall, less budgetary allocation has impacted most of the child health programmes.', 'Move to pre-emptive care model where the focus and thrust will be on child health and prevention', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'move-to-pre-emptive-care-model-where-the-focus-and-thrust-will-be-on-child-health-and-prevention', '', '', '2017-05-18 08:35:34', '2017-05-18 03:05:34', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=621', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
