(626, 7, '2017-05-18 08:38:05', '2017-05-18 03:08:05', 'In India, numerous regulatory bodies viz Medical Council of India (MCI), Pharmacy Council of India, Central Drugs Standard Control Organisation are working in healthcare sector. In 2016, Parliament passed <a href="http://www.prsindia.org/billtrack/the-indian-medical-council-amendment-bill-2016-4343/">Indian Medical Council (Amendment) Act</a>, which has changes pertaining to a uniform entrance examination. No other provision regarding review of role of MCI exists in this Act. Government hasn’t taken any steps to setup an overarching lean body for healthcare.', 'Will review the role of various professional regulatory bodies in healthcare and consider setting up an overarching lean body for healthcare', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'will-review-the-role-of-various-professional-regulatory-bodies-in-healthcare-and-consider-setting-up-an-overarching-lean-body-for-healthcare', '', '', '2017-05-18 08:38:05', '2017-05-18 03:08:05', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=626', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
