(631, 7, '2017-05-18 08:43:19', '2017-05-18 03:13:19', '<a href="http://www.prsindia.org/uploads/media/AIIMS/The%20AIIMS%20(A)%20Bill,%202012.pdf">All India Institute of Medical Sciences (Amendment) Act, 2012</a> introduced 6 new AIIMS in the country, other than the one at New Delhi. <a href="http://pmssy-mohfw.nic.in/listofcolleges.aspx">Four new AIIMS</a> at Andhra Pradesh, Uttar Pradesh, Maharashtra and West Bengal were announced in Budget, 2014-15 and their funds were approved by the Cabinet. However, they are still in early construction stages. <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/mbErel.aspx?relid=123410">6 new AIIMS were announced during Budget Speech 2015-16</a>, all of which are in the stage of site finalisation. In the most recent Budget, 2017-18, Finance Minister announced setting up of <a href="http://www.financialexpress.com/budget/union-budget-2017-fm-arun-jaitley-said-two-new-aiims-will-be-set-up-in-jharkhand-and-gujarat/532455/">two more AIIMS in Jharkhand and Gujarat</a>.', 'Will set up an AIIMS like institute in every state', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'will-set-up-an-aiims-like-institute-in-every-state', '', '', '2017-05-18 08:43:19', '2017-05-18 03:13:19', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=631', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
