(662, 3, '2017-05-18 12:16:15', '2017-05-18 06:46:15', 'The BJP government <a href="http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/msp-50-percent-more-than-agriculture-produce-s-cost-can-distort-market-115022001360_1.html">has not accepted</a> the Standing Committee recommendation of keeping MSP (Minimum Support Price) at least 50% more than the cost of production, saying doing so may distort the market.\r\n\r\nNo steps have been taken <a href="http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/telangana-urges-centre-to-link-mgnrega-to-agriculture/articleshow/58297144.cms">for linking MNREGA to agriculture.</a>', 'Ensure a minimum of 50% profit over the cost of production by revising the Minimum Support Price and increase farmer profitability by linking MNREGA to agriculture', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ensure-a-minimum-of-50-profit-over-the-cost-of-production-by-revising-the-minimum-support-price-and-increase-farmer-profitability-by-linking-mnrega-to-agriculture', '', '', '2017-05-18 12:16:15', '2017-05-18 06:46:15', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=662', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
