(664, 3, '2017-05-18 12:18:07', '2017-05-18 06:48:07', 'No new scheme has been launched by the government to introduce rotational farming.\r\n\r\nThe promotion of herbal products comes under the ministry of AYUSH. The ministry of AYUSH was set up by the BJP government to promote herbal medicines and plants. However, the <a href="http://www.ayush.gov.in/sites/default/files/ANNUAL%20R%20EPORT%202016-17%20ENGLISH.pdf">sale</a> of herbal medicines has decreased from Rs 36 crores in 2013-14 to Rs 34 crores in 2015-16.', 'Introduce rotation farming for herbal products, based on the geographical mapping, to enhance the income of farmers', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'introduce-rotation-farming-for-herbal-products-based-on-the-geographical-mapping-to-enhance-the-income-of-farmers', '', '', '2017-05-18 12:18:07', '2017-05-18 06:48:07', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=664', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
