(673, 3, '2017-05-18 12:39:51', '2017-05-18 07:09:51', 'The BJP government launched a television channel dedicated to Farmers (<a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=122039">DD Kisan</a>) in May 2015. Viewership of the channel is around <a href="http://www.indiantelevision.com/television/tv-channels/terrestrial/dd-kisan-viewership-is-72m-a-month-received-rs-800m-govt-funds-for-17-18-170408">73 lakh per month</a> on average. Funds allocated for the channel has increased from<a href="http://www.indiantelevision.com/television/tv-channels/terrestrial/dd-kisan-viewership-is-72m-a-month-received-rs-800m-govt-funds-for-17-18-170408"> Rs. 26 crores in 2014-15 to Rs. 70 crores in 2016-17</a>. The programmes are <a href="http://164.100.47.190/loksabhaquestions/annex/10/AS390.pdf">translated into regional languages</a> by other Doordarshan Kendras.\n\nHowever, no regional Kisan TV channels have been set up. Hence, region specific and in-depth information is not delivered to farmers in real time.', 'Explore setting up of regional Kisan TV channels', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '562-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-05-18 12:39:51', '2017-05-18 07:09:51', '', 562, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/562-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
