(702, 3, '2017-05-18 13:24:49', '2017-05-18 07:54:49', 'The expenditure limit for contesting Lok Sabha Elections is Rs. 70 Lakh. It means that no candidate can legally spend more than Rs. 70 Lakh on his/her election campaign. However, no action has been taken to revise this limit thus far.', 'Look at revising expenditure limits realistically', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'look-at-revising-expenditure-limits-realistically', '', '', '2017-05-18 23:38:42', '2017-05-18 18:08:42', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=702', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
