(710, 7, '2017-05-18 13:33:06', '2017-05-18 08:03:06', 'India’s demographic dividend is contingent upon the healthcare and education facilities provided to it. Hence, a coherent National Health Policy becomes crucial. <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=159376">Union Cabinet approved the National Health Policy, 2017</a> in its meeting on March 15<sup>th,</sup> 2017\r\n\r\nThe <a href="http://mohfw.gov.in/showfile.php?lid=4275">policy</a> is comprehensive in its approach and robustly covers all aspects of healthcare. However, some aspects of the policy needs to be discussed and debated. It has set target to achieve a life expectancy of 70 years by 2025, while in 2015 India has a life expectancy of 68.3. The contours of India’s health care delivery majorly depends on its health expenditure.\r\n\r\nThe policy is silent on the measures to increase the health expenditure of government to 2.5% of GDP by 2025.', 'Initiate the New Health Policy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '585-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-05-18 13:33:06', '2017-05-18 08:03:06', '', 585, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/585-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(711, 7, '2017-05-18 13:38:28', '2017-05-18 08:08:28', '<a href="https://thewire.in/106575/health-budget-2017-18/">Budgetary allocation to National Rural Health M<u>ission (NRHM)</u></a>, as total percentage of total health budget has fallen from 52.6% in 2015-16 to 43.4% in 2017-18. Under NRHM, the share of ‘Infrastructure maintenance’ has constantly fallen from <a href="https://thewire.in/106575/health-budget-2017-18/">28.5% in 2015-16 to 26% in 2017-18.</a> Low budgetary allocation will impede the progress of modernisation and upgradation of health infrastructure.\r\n\r\nGovernment launched many apps like <a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=155854">Swachh Bharat app, ANM Online Application(ANMOL), Kilkari</a>, etc and initiated other digital platforms like <a href="https://www.nhp.gov.in/">National Health Portal</a>, <a href="http://ors.gov.in/index.html">Online Registration System</a>, to bring latest technologies in healthcare sector.', 'Modernize Government hospitals, upgrading infrastructure and latest technologies', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '623-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-18 13:38:28', '2017-05-18 08:08:28', '', 623, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/623-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(712, 3, '2017-05-18 13:56:02', '2017-05-18 08:26:02', 'No government order or legislation has been issued that makes it mandatory for the government to digitise government work. Therefore, the promise has been classified as "Yet to Start".', 'Mandate digitization of all government work to reduce corruption and delays', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'mandate-digitization-of-all-government-work-to-reduce-corruption-and-delays', '', '', '2017-05-18 23:10:07', '2017-05-18 17:40:07', '', 0, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/?post_type=promise&#038;p=712', 0, 'promise', '', 0),
(713, 7, '2017-05-18 13:55:34', '2017-05-18 08:25:34', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">To promote bilateral cooperation with other countries, government has </span><a href="http://msme.gov.in/sites/default/files/IC_EN.pdf"><span style="font-weight: 400;">continued International Cooperation Scheme</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> in the 12th Year Plan with an outlay of Rs. 24 Crores.</span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">BJP government</span><a href="http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/small-biz/policy-trends/india-finalises-mou-on-msme-cooperation-with-iora-nations/articleshow/56687790.cms"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">finalised Memorandum of Understanding (MoU) </span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> on MSME corporations with Indian Ocean Rim Association (IORA) nations to share best practices &amp; innovation in January, 2017. It is yet to sign the MoU.</span>', 'Provide international linkages for exports in MSME sector', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '515-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-05-18 13:55:34', '2017-05-18 08:25:34', '', 515, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/515-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
