(732, 7, '2017-05-18 14:05:27', '2017-05-18 08:35:27', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">No special courts have been set up to stop hoarding and black marketeering. No progress has been made with regard to the amendment making </span><a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=107453"><span style="font-weight: 400;">hoarding a non-bailable offence</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">No strict measure has been initiated by the government. Their steps, thus far, are limited to issuing </span><a href="http://pib.nic.in/newsite/mbErel.aspx?relid=121420"><span style="font-weight: 400;">advisories to State governments </span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">for strict enforcement of essential Commodities Act, 1955, and the Prime Minister </span><a href="http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Set-up-special-courts-to-try-hoarders-PM-Narendra-Modi-tells-states/articleshow/37282089.cms"><span style="font-weight: 400;">urging</span></a> <span style="font-weight: 400;">the States to  set up special courts. </span>', 'Put in place strict measures and special courts to stop hoarding and black marketing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '394-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-18 14:05:27', '2017-05-18 08:35:27', '', 394, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/394-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(733, 7, '2017-05-18 14:06:10', '2017-05-18 08:36:10', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">No considerable progress has been made with regard to doubling the number of courts and judges in sub-ordinate judiciary. The sanctioned strength of judges in district and sub-ordinate courts has increased from </span><a href="http://supremecourtofindia.nic.in/courtnews/2014_issue_2.pdf"><span style="font-weight: 400;">19,726</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> to </span><a href="http://supremecourtofindia.nic.in/courtnews/2016_issue_3.pdf"><span style="font-weight: 400;">21,374,</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> an increase of mere 8% against the promise of 100%.</span>', 'Double the number of courts and judges in the subordinate judiciary in a phased manner', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '367-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-05-18 14:06:10', '2017-05-18 08:36:10', '', 367, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/367-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
