(791, 1, '2017-05-19 00:28:04', '2017-05-18 18:58:04', '<p>[et_pb_section bb_built="1" admin_label="section" background_color="#00a06b" inner_shadow="on" fullwidth="on" transparent_background="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="on" make_equal="off" use_custom_gutter="off"][et_pb_fullwidth_header admin_label="Fullwidth Header" title="Our Team" text_orientation="justified" background_layout="dark" header_fullscreen="off" header_scroll_down="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" content_orientation="center" image_orientation="center" custom_button_one="off" button_one_letter_spacing="0" button_one_use_icon="default" button_one_icon_placement="right" button_one_on_hover="on" button_one_letter_spacing_hover="0" custom_button_two="off" button_two_letter_spacing="0" button_two_use_icon="default" button_two_icon_placement="right" button_two_on_hover="on" button_two_letter_spacing_hover="0"]</p><p>Election Promises Tracker is an initiative of a group of citizens connected by their love for democracy.</p><p>[/et_pb_fullwidth_header][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built="1" admin_label="section" fullwidth="off" specialty="off"][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Anurag Kundu" position="Co-Founder" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/pp-1-200x200.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" facebook_url="https://www.facebook.com/anurag.kundu" twitter_url="https://twitter.com/anuragkunduak?lang=en" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_css_member_image="{|| height: 250px !important; width:250px;||}"]</p><p><strong>Anurag </strong>works with Ministry of Education, Government of Delhi. He was preciously involved in the drafting of Education Manifesto of Aam Aadmi Party for Delhi Elections 2015.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Anup Kalbalia" position="Co-Founder" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/16473714_1617510591609009_9073309239860008602_n-250x182.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" facebook_url="https://www.facebook.com/search/top/?q=anup%20kalbalia" twitter_url="https://twitter.com/anupkal?lang=en" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_css_member_image=" { height: 100px;|| width: 100px; }"]</p><p><strong>Anup </strong>works with Directi, a software products company. In his free time he likes to meet people over a cup of coffee, a mug of beer or a few glasses fresh fruit juices to discuss politics.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Rashmi Singh" position="Lead Researcher" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/10014530_983031268392169_5083362588198484624_n-250x185-1.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" facebook_url="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=1303472202" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p><strong>Rashmi Singh</strong> is passionate about politics and yearns to strengthen democracy. A student of economics and a Teach For India fellow, she seeks to lead a meaningful life.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Vipul Goyal" position="Lead, Processes and Personnel " image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/13094270_10154220485348436_4482630848393449287_n-188x250.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" facebook_url="https://www.facebook.com/vipul.goyal" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>A graduate from IIT Kanpur, Vipul spent his last 3 years teaching in a marginalized community in Delhi.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Robin Keshaw" position="Lead, Partnerships &amp; Expansion" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/12510264_10153752295005937_1406509919520404726_n-223x250-223x250.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>Robin Keshaw is Assignment Editor with NTI Media. He writes on development issues and policies. A computer science engineer from BITS, Pilani, he taught in an socially and economically community in Delhi as a Teach for India fellow. When he is not ''adulting'', you can find him teaching kids, writing poetry or trekking in mountains.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Himanshu Gulati" position="Researcher" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/10155462_642238059200590_2134138735067742745_n-250x250.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>Himanshu Gulati is an educator and helps kids enjoy Physics. Being agnostic, he could be find talking about religion, politics and theory. An observer, poet and finding the best ways to lead a fit life enthusiast, he is trying hands at Photography these days.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Shubham Sarin" position="Lead, Technology" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/13062350_1171502076216586_2696804551449870711_n-250x182.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>Shubham currently works as a Software Engineer at Paytm.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Sajal Singh" position="Fact Checker" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/18157323_10210986115722890_128516437352806744_n-158x250.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>Sajal is a politics enthusiast. A post graduate in Economics, he loves to debate and discuss politically incorrect issues and believes that nothing should be taboo in a mature democracy. He has been associated with a number of education start ups the most prominent being civilsdaily.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Vidur Khanna" position="Technology" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/13592756_1019941838102778_7998836317871435894_n-198x198.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>Vidur graduated from NIT Kurukshetra and currently works with PayTM.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Shriram" position="Intern" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/11905774_932163730231454_9106338492012823653_n-250x160.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>Shriram is a graduate in Chemistry from St. Stephen''s College, Delhi.</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][et_pb_team_member admin_label="Team Member" name="Munish Kaushik" position="Metor" image_url="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/pp-250x250.jpg" animation="fade_in" background_layout="light" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]</p><p>Munish is a development professional with a child-like heart. He has 16 years of experience of working for Child Rights and Disaster Management. He works with Delhi Government in education and participatory governance related projects. He has a really cool website. Do check out: http://www.munshiinpublicservice.com</p><p>[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]</p>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '789-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-05-19 00:28:04', '2017-05-18 18:58:04', '', 789, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/789-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
