" button_on_hover="on" button_letter_spacing_hover="0" background_color="#313f55" body_line_height="2.4em"] [/et_pb_post_slider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built="1" admin_label="section" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off"][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_divider admin_label="Divider" color="#27323a" show_divider="on" height="5" divider_style="solid" divider_position="top" hide_on_mobile="on"] [/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="row" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="on" use_custom_gutter="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_equal="off" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="off" parallax_2="off" parallax_method_2="off"][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_image admin_label="Image" src="http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Promises-1.png" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" animation="left" use_overlay="off" sticky="off" align="left" force_fullwidth="off" always_center_on_mobile="on" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"] [/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_text admin_label="Text" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n<h1>What we do!</h1>\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Monitor Government Progress" url_new_window="off" use_icon="on" font_icon="%%160%%" icon_color="#ffffff" use_circle="on" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#2ea3f2" icon_placement="left" animation="top" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center" circle_color="#2ea3f2" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\r\nOur effort is to enable voters to monitor the performance of their governments. We will also assess if governments adhere to all of their promises in regard to education, health, economy,agriculture, transparency, law and order, minority rights, culture, and many more.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Fact-Check Claims" url_new_window="off" use_icon="on" font_icon="%%49%%" icon_color="#ffffff" use_circle="on" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#2ea3f2" icon_placement="left" animation="top" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center" url="Fact checking any statement or claim issued by our elected representatives. No opinion, Only 100% verified Facts" circle_color="#2ea3f2" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\r\nFact checking any statement or claim issued by our elected representatives. No opinion, Only 100% verified Facts\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label="Blurb" title="Discuss &amp; Spread" url_new_window="off" use_icon="on" font_icon="%%222%%" icon_color="#ffffff" use_circle="on" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#2ea3f2" icon_placement="left" animation="top" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center" circle_color="#2ea3f2" use_icon_font_size="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n\r\nEnable community dialogue, and help spread right information to the world.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built="1" admin_label="section" fullwidth="off" specialty="off" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off"][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_divider admin_label="Divider" color="#27323a" show_divider="on" height="30" divider_style="solid" divider_position="top" hide_on_mobile="on"] [/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="Row"][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_text admin_label="Text" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]\r\n<h1>Our Vision!</h1>\r\nTo track every government on every sector by 2020. This is a work in progress and we require your help in tracking the performance of the rest of the state and localgovernments. If you share our love for democracy, please write to us atjoinus@electionpromisestracker.in and will figure out ways of collaboration.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built="1" admin_label="section" fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_color="#313f55" inner_shadow="on" parallax="off" transparent_background="off" allow_player_pause="off" parallax_method="off" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="on" make_equal="off" use_custom_gutter="off"][et_pb_row admin_label="row"][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_cta admin_label="Call To Action" button_url="#" button_text="Register" use_background_color="on" background_color="#313f55" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="center" title="Subscribe to Our Updates!" url_new_window="off" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_button="off" button_letter_spacing="0" button_use_icon="default" button_icon_placement="right" button_on_hover="on" button_letter_spacing_hover="0"]\r\n\r\nRegister here to receive email notifications about our latest updates!\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '36-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-18 16:20:09', '2017-05-18 10:50:09', '', 36, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/36-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
