(807, 3, '2017-05-18 17:36:27', '2017-05-18 12:06:27', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">BJP government set up Custom Clearance </span><a href="http://www.business-standard.com/article/pti-stories/govt-sets-up-ccfcs-at-ports-to-expedite-customs-clearance-115070700626_1.html"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Facilitation Centres</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> (CCFCs) at major Indian seaports &amp; Airports in July 2015 to ensure easier clearances. A </span><a href="http://www.cbec.gov.in/htdocs-cbec/customs/cs-circulars/cs-circulars-2015/circ-13-2015cs"><span style="font-weight: 400;">committee</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> was formed with immediate effect from April 2015. </span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">CBEC (Central Board of Excise &amp; Customs) launched Single window interface for facilitating Trade (</span><a href="http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/economy/indian-customs-launches-swift-clearances/article8426720.ece"><span style="font-weight: 400;">SWIFT</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">) in April 2016 for quick single window custom clearances  for import. The </span><a href="https://www.icegate.gov.in/SWIFT/index.html"><span style="font-weight: 400;">portal</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> has been operational under CBEC website.</span>', 'Set up trade facilitation to ensure easier customs clearances', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '512-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-05-18 17:36:27', '2017-05-18 12:06:27', '', 512, 'http://www.electionpromisestracker.in/512-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
